{"tid":143494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"生於香港為男人，犯賤是基本","createTime":"2017-03-04T16:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T16:37:45.000Z","uid":4623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f323a0742a0a3712c373b2483edd6ad68631360b","tid":143494,"uid":4623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:06:10.000Z","msg":"有個女仔<br />\n性格開朗<br />\n唔係好靚嗰種<br />\n係笑得好甜<br />\n小小萌嘅特質<br />\n我鐘意咗佢<br />\n佢啲朋友好八婆<br />\n鐘意對人評頭論足<br />\n係都搵嘢嚟恥笑你<br />\n我每日就只可以隔住班八婆<br />\n望住你<br />\n有時我地四目交接<br />\n你笑一笑<br />\n我又笑一笑<br />\n如果世界停留係呢刻幾好<br />\n我知你有鍾意嘅人<br />\n佢係完美嘅生存證據<br />\n但都係好想擁有你<br />\n希望有一日佢會睇到你幾好<br />\n好似我睇你咁好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝你幸福<br />\n連兵都不如嘅過客"},{"pid":"59e9bc0fb4b3df8f386398e3fb3d42ef5b109805","tid":143494,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"咩歌？"},{"pid":"c142257195b756ff73740ea86de22c409f6e59e7","tid":143494,"uid":55997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:11:14.000Z","msg":"天涯過客"},{"pid":"ec8f8a5fc574656348e56d3b7c68f15aaf606519","tid":143494,"uid":4623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩歌？</blockquote><br />\n心聲非歌但能聽到韻律"},{"pid":"2c42f760640cb6909ead69414fb555794d131082","tid":143494,"uid":4623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:37:45.000Z","msg":"難離也總要捨<br />\n你不想恨心<br />\n我只好無情"}]}